feedinfo.name: abuse.ch_feodo
feedinfo.summary: Feodo Tracker is a project of abuse.ch with the goal of sharing botnet C&C servers associated with Dridex, Emotet (aka Heodo), TrickBot, QakBot (aka QuakBot / Qbot) and BazarLoader (aka BazarBackdoor). It offers various blocklists, helping network owners to protect their users from Dridex and Emotet/Heodo.
